Class AbstractTraceIdFilter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • teetime.framework.AbstractStage
      • teetime.framework.AbstractConsumerStage<T>
        • kieker.analysis.stage.select.traceidfilter.components.AbstractTraceIdFilter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type parameter for specific record types.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OperationExecutionTraceIdFilter, TraceEventTraceIdFilter, TraceMetadataTraceIdFilter

    public abstract class AbstractTraceIdFilter<T>
extends teetime.framework.AbstractConsumerStage<T>
    Abstract class which describes internal components of TraceIdFilterOld. Each concrete component filters the trace ids of a specific record type T.
    Since:
    1.2
    Author:
    Andre van Hoorn, Jan Waller, Lars Bluemke
